  <scopecontent id="aspace_0d6d6c26eae1c042ee352233cf0d2fcd">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Collection is mostly a file of jobs done by the Platts. Also includes insurance records, paid bills, cancelled checks, and blueprints and drawings.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_76eece3fcb160e090a0e7fefb4d62f85">
